{"tid":673163,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲成峰高教：公司沒有購入任何土地","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T06:04:42.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60d47707b304c08a05a0f9d7369de2acec70e054","tid":673163,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"香港電台<br />\n<br />\n澳洲成峰高教否認有報道指，公司已經簽約購買兩幅土地，並預期分別於2019年及2022年交付。<br />\n<br />\n公司發澄清公告指並沒有購入任何土地，不過與澳洲科技園業主之一，Mirvac Projects，就澳洲科技園未來租賃訂立兩項租賃建議。按照目前計劃，並考慮到招股章程所列的因素，有關新租賃地點預料分別於明年6月及2020年8月前投入作校園使用。<br />\n<br />\n公司股價今日急升41%，收報0.82元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/澳洲成峰高教-01752-於澳洲科技園訂立兩項租賃協議-130929997.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%88%90%E5%B3%B0%E9%AB%98%E6%95%99-01752-%E6%96%BC%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%9C%92%E8%A8%82%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%A9%E9%A0%85%E7%A7%9F%E8%B3%83%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-130929997.html&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=47fb38e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/澳洲成峰高教-01752-於澳洲科技園訂立兩項租賃協議-130929997.html</a>"},{"pid":"1e515ebf3e227eb7aab0734f994a4584b61a1162","tid":673163,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2018/0521/LTN20180521778_C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2018%2F0521%2FLTN20180521778_C.pdf&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f8c05a1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2018/0521/LTN20180521778_C.pdf</a>"}]}